pre_pr_migrator_status.python39: not solvable: ['Encountered problems while solving.\nProblem: package numpy-1.19.1-py36h5510c5b_0 requires python >=3.6,<3.7.0a0, but none of the providers can be installed\n']

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.3.0" %}

package:
  name: cell_tree2d
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/NOAA-ORR-ERD/cell_tree2d/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 4a5759951f67a3ff199137c87bb565b1897541130de5a4a2067acb22b0f39bae

build:
  number: 1006
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - cython
    - numpy
  run:
    - python
    - numpy

test:
  requires:
    - pytest
  imports:
    - cell_tree2d
  commands:
    - py.test --pyargs cell_tree2d

about:
  home: https://github.com/NOAA-ORR-ERD/cell_tree2d
  license: Public Domain
  summary: 'CellTree data structure as described by Garth and Joy 2010.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - ChrisBarker-NOAA
    - jay-hennen
